originalText.text: Food I ordered basic chicken tenders that were not cooked all the way. The Buffalo wings were way to saucy. Definitely a grown and sophisticated crowd. RESPONSE: WE can discuss

The empanadas and chicken wings was super delicious!! The ambiance and the music was Superb! Me and my family/friends will definitely patronize this fantastic place again!! Thank You so much Inkwell for making my hubby‚Äôs birthday the best day ever!!!

originalText.text: I didn't want a big party this year. I just wanted  to hear some good music in a good atmosphere. So me and my sister decided to go to club Inkwell. We reserved a table at a reasonable price and it came with a dozen of cup cakes. They had red velvet and that was a plus. From the door the hospitality was excellent. The chicken and empanadas were delicious. D.J. Mike C did his thing. He shouted me and everyone else all night. The bartenders know how to make a drink and were very nice.  Oh and they had two for one drinks.  Kevin and the whole inkwell crew really made my night. They gave me a birthday crown and surrounded me with flashing lights, sparkles and so much love. It really melted my heart. Everything was sooo perfect and I really enjoyed myself. My sister danced more than me. She couldn't sit down. She's already talking about going to see Michel'le perform on February16th. She went crazy when I sent her the info. V.I.P.  area was on point. Very clean and nice. Nice mature crowd. I will be going back in 2 weeks. Thank you Kevin and the whole Inkwell staff. You all made my birthday soooo special. Excellent job!!!!! üëèüôå Happy New Year and you will see me next year.
